playstore_details.title: Simplicity Browser: Fast & Secure
playstore_details.description:
Simplicity is a new browser for Android built with speed, privacy and security in mind.

Features:

-Bookmarks
-Ad-blocker
-Do not track
-Full-screen video support 
-Private mode
-Desktop mode
-Reader mode (coming soon)
-Tabs
-Plugins

Source code here:  https://github.com/creativetrendsapps/SimplicityBrowser
